li%3EElon%20Musk%20says%20self-driving%20cars%20only%20need%20to%20rely%20on%20cameras%2C%20and%20not%20other%20sensors%20like%20LiDAR.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20Rivian%20CEO%20RJ%20Scaringe%20says%20LiDAR%20is%20%26quot%3Bdefinitely%20beneficial.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EScaringe%20said%20LiDAR%20has%20become%20much%20cheaper%20over%20the%20years%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bcan%20do%20things%20that%20cameras%20can't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERivian%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frivian-ceo-china-evs-low-cost-competition-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERJ%20Scaringe%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20his%20company%20has%20a%20different%20view%20on%20LiDAR%20and%20its%20relevance%20to%20achieving%20autonomous%20driving%20than%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20view%20is%20that%20it's%20definitely%20beneficial%2C%20and%20our%20approach%20to%20sensors%20has%20been%20that%20we%20need%20to%20rapidly%20build%20our%20foundation%20model%20as%20fast%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Scaringe%20told%20The%20Verge's%20%26quot%3BDecoder%26quot%3B%20podcast%20in%20an%20episode%20that%20aired%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScaringe%20told%20guest%20host%20and%20journalist%20Joanna%20Stern%20that%20there%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Breal%20benefit%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bwouldn't%20rule%20out%26quot%3B%20including%20it%20in%20a%20self-driving%20vehicle's%20multi-sensor%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20over%20LiDAR%20started%20during%20an%20earlier%20development%20period%2C%20when%20the%20models%20being%20run%20had%20trouble%20processing%20inputs%20from%20different%20sensors%20and%20cameras%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20what's%20happened%20is%20that%20we%20no%20longer%20run%20the%20models%20like%20that.%20So%20the%20models%20benefit%20from%20the%20maximum%20amount%20of%20information%20on%20the%20front%20of%20the%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20Scaringe%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cost%20of%20LiDAR%20used%20to%20be%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars.%20It's%20now%20low%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20hundred%20bucks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20really%20great%20sensor%20that%20can%20do%20things%20that%20cameras%20can't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Scaringe%20at%20Rivian%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScaringe's%20view%20differs%20from%20that%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20has%20repeatedly%20criticized%20LiDAR%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20Musk%20said%20in%20an%20X%20post%20that%20using%20LiDAR%20and%20radar%20alongside%20cameras%20results%20in%20%26quot%3Bsensor%20contention.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20sensor%20ambiguity%20causes%20increased%2C%20not%20decreased%2C%20risk.%20That's%20why%20Waymos%20can't%20drive%20on%20highways%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20on%20X%20on%20August%2025%2C%20referencing%20the%20robotaxi%20service%20owned%20by%20Google's%20parent%20company%2C%20Alphabet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaymo's%20self-driving%20vehicles%20use%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-robotaxi-lidar-sensor-versus-cameras-vision-only-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emulti-sensor%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20comprising%20LiDAR%2C%20radar%2C%20and%20cameras%20to%20perceive%20their%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20is%20instead%20betting%20its%20hopes%20on%20a%20vision-only%20system%20that%20relies%20on%20cameras%2C%20Musk%20said%20at%20Tesla's%20%26quot%3BAutonomy%20Day%26quot%3B%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20cars%2C%20it's%20friggin%20stupid.%20It's%20expensive%20and%20unnecessary.%20Once%20you%20solve%20vision%2C%20it's%20worthless%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScaringe%20isn't%20the%20only%20auto%20executive%20who%20disagrees%20with%20Musk%20on%20LiDAR.%20In%20June%2C%20F