%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20just%20three%20carry-ons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Carey%20and%20Demir%20Bentley%20with%20luggage%20when%20they%20moved%20to%20Bali.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e34b701c1f80efbec4f5ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%202016%2C%20Carey%20and%20Demir%20moved%20to%20Ubud%2C%20Bali%2C%20with%20three%20carry-ons.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Carey%20Bentley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f370685a-8cf6-41ce-a4ea-9afc5a55c97d%5C%22%3EWe%20started%20the%20business%20in%20Bali%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%2C%20we%20discovered%20an%20entrepreneurial%20community%2C%20a%20slower%20pace%2C%20and%20a%20more%20sustainable%20lifestyle.%20It%20was%20the%20reset%20we%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20business%20that%20would%20allow%20us%20to%20live%20fully%2C%20work%20smarter%2C%20and%20help%20others%20do%20the%20same.%20That's%20how%20the%20Lifehack%20Method%20was%20born%20%E2%80%94%20coaching%20professionals%20to%20achieve%20more%20without%20burning%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20days%2C%20Demir%20was%20up%20at%204%20a.m.%20for%20global%20calls%20while%20I%20ran%20digital%20marketing.%20It%20was%20intense%2C%20but%20we%20thrived%20on%20testing%2C%20listening%2C%20and%20refining.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-bali-workcation-struggles-work-tourists-friends-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBali's%20culture%20of%20balance%3C%2Fa%3E%20shaped%20our%20company's%20philosophy.%20People%20we%20met%20in%20Bali%20didn't%20work%20all%20day%3B%20they%20made%20time%20for%20family%2C%20community%2C%20and%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20corporate%20world%20obsessed%20with%20hustle%2C%20this%20was%20a%20radical%20shift.%20We%20integrated%20that%20mindset%20into%20our%20work%20with%20clients%2C%20helping%20them%20create%20schedules%20that%20protected%20their%20health%20and%20allowed%20room%20for%20joy.%20While%20living%20in%20Bali%2C%20we%20even%20had%20time%20to%20take%20side%20trips%20to%20India%2C%20Singapore%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20Thailand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESettling%20into%20our%20new%20home%20was%20an%20adventure%20in%20itself.%20Getting%20around%20meant%20navigating%20chaotic%20streets%20on%20scooters%2C%20and%20the%20humidity%20hit%20like%20a%20wall.%20Rainstorms%20were%20a%20daily%20surprise%2C%20so%20we%20always%20had%20ponchos%20ready.%20But%20the%20rewards%20included%20great%20food%2C%20daily%20coffee%20rituals%2C%20and%20a%20perfectly%20unhurried%20pace%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Carey%20and%20Demir%20Bentley%20started%20their%20family%20in%20Medell%C3%ADn%2C%20Colombia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e34c481c1f80efbec4f5b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20started%20their%20family%20in%20Medell%C3%ADn%2C%20Colombia%20%E2%80%94%20Bentley%20was%20impressed%20by%20the%20local%20healthcare%20system.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Carey%20Bentley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a46437eb-8606-4fb1-add1-7920f09e1da1%5C%22%3EOur%20business%20prompted%20us%20to%20relocate%20again%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20our%20company%20grew%2C%20the%20Asia-US%20time%20difference%20became%20harder%20to%20manage.%20In%202019%2C%20we%20chose%20to%20relocate%20to%20Medell%C3%ADn%2C%20Colombia.%20It%20was%20a%20place%20we%20hadn't%20explored%20before%2C%20but%20one%20that%20aligned%20better%20with%20our%20US-based%20clients.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdream-trip-to-bali-disappointing-changed-plans-save-it-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELeaving%20Bali%20was%20bittersweet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20Medell%C3%ADn%20quickly%20won%20us%20over%20with%20its%20modern%20amenities%20and%20family-focused%20culture.%20It%20was%20easy%20to%20feel%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20welcomed%20our%20first%20daughter%20in%202019%2C%20followed%20by%20two%20more%20in%202022%20and%202024.%20The%20Colombian%20healthcare%20system%20was%20exceptional%2C%20and%20the%20at-home%20support%20we%20received%20was%20beyond%20what%20we%20would%20have%20found%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20couldn't%20have%20asked%20for%20a%20better%20environment%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbali-raising-kids-crowded-tourists-expats-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eraise%20our%20children%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Our%20kids%20were%20learning%20Spanish%2C%20immersed%20in%20two%20vibrant%20cultures.%20Our%20community%20%E2%80%94%20both%20local%20and%20expat%20%E2%80%94%20was%20a%20lifeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Carey%20Bentley%20and%20her%20three%20kids%20and%20dog%20in%20Atlanta.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e34d061c1f80efbec4f5bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222736%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%202024%2C%20the%20couple%20moved%20back%20to%20the%20US%20to%20raise%20their%20kids%20and%20be%20closer%20to%20family.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Carey%20Bentley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f0336c43-d283-40f5-9f4d-8d5d4f5a342e%5C%22%3EFamily%20ties%20pulled%20us%20back%20to%20the%20US%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20our%20family%20grew%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20our%20aging%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20October%2C%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-moved-home-after-living-abroad-culture-shocks-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20back%20to%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20settled%20in%20a%20walkable%2C%20rural%20community%20outside%20Atlanta.%20Life%20here%20is%20faster%20than%20our%20years%20abroad%2C%20but%20it's%20given%20us%20the%20chance%20to%20build%20a%20village%